title: War of the Roses: Canoodling with a Co-worker at the Airport
description: Becca's friend texted her saying she saw her husband at the airport getting a little too cozy with another woman.  She sent pictures and everything to show her. AND gift cards have started to go missing.  Who is the woman Becca's husband was getting too comfortable with and was it harmful or harmless?
